'''Priority Sector High Commander''' was a high [[Rank insignia plaque/Legends|rank]] in the [[Republic Military/Legends|Republic]] and [[Imperial Military/Legends|Imperial Military]]. During the reorganization of the Imperial Military caused by the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|destruction]] of the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]] over [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]], the temporary rank insignia possessed six blue squares at the top, three red squares on the bottom left, and three orange squares on the bottom right, similar in appearance to one version of the [[Grand Moff/Legends|Grand Moff]] plaque rank.

==Behind the scenes==
The rank of Priority Sector High Commander was the highest given [[Rank insignia plaque/Legends|rank]] of the ''[[Imperial Sourcebook]]'', although its exact powers were not specified.

